---
title: Lemon-Roasted Tilapia with Provençale Sauté
description: Take a trip to the south of France with this Provence-inspired recipe! Herbs de Provence is a fragrant mix of lavender, thyme, marjoram, savory, oregano, and rosemary. It perfumes the dish with a unique floral aroma. Bon appétit!
